port order \n     performance level is as follows:\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n       ``If the support order performance level is:              The\n-----------------------------------------------------------  applicable\n                                                But less     percentage\n                  At least:                       than:          is:\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n80%.........................................  ............          100\n79%.........................................          80%            98\n78%.........................................          79%            96\n77%.........................................          78%            94\n76%.........................................          77%            92\n75%.........................................          76%            90\n74%.........................................          75%            88\n73%.........................................          74%            86\n72%.........................................          73%            84\n71%.........................................          72%            82\n70%.........................................          71%            80\n69%.........................................          70%            79\n68%.........................................          69%            78\n67%.........................................          68%            77\n66%.........................................          67%            76\n65%.........................................          66%            75\n64%.........................................          65%            74\n63%.........................................          64%            73\n62%.........................................          63%            72\n61%.........................................          62%            71\n60%.........................................        